969
00:55:40,375 --> 00:55:43,208
No. It was just a misunderstanding.

970
00:55:43,833 --> 00:55:46,333
If it became true,

971
00:55:46,708 --> 00:55:49,916
Your parents would be the most devastated.

972
00:56:02,541 --> 00:56:06,041
Sappitiyo Wiwach Chantu.

