00:56:40,041 --> 00:56:42,291
I'm getting better, right?

985
00:56:43,333 --> 00:56:46,125
How's Steve, Vinai?

986
00:56:46,791 --> 00:56:47,958
Is he doing better?

987
00:56:50,000 --> 00:56:52,583
